These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, family, action, zombie
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, trike, snowmobile
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the trike##2
6. the person watching zombie movies is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | comedy     | action | family |
| Transport     | bus     | trike | snowmobile  | quad-bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, trance, electronic, house
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike, bike, skateboard
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of house is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | pop | trance    | house     | electronic  |
| Transport     | scooter    | bike | motorbike | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, classical, indie, r&b
4 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
2. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
5. the owner of the horse is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | classical   | indie   | metal  | r&b |
| Pet           | chinchilla | mouse | horse | dog  |

