.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, cooking, hiking, writing
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, australian, italian, chinese
1. the chinese is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the italian##2
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the italian is on the left or right of the chinese##3
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the spanish is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | cooking | woodworking | writing | hiking  |
| Nationality   | australian  | spanish   | chinese  | italian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, sprite, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, skydiving, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | milk    | tea   | sprite | mirinda    |
| Hobby      | video-games | rock-climbing | skydiving       | sudoku |

