.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, iced-tea, mirinda
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, jet-ski, quad-bike, car
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the car and the person drinking iced-tea##2
3. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | mirinda | lemonade |
| Transport   | jet-ski | snowmobile  | quad-bike    | car  |

