.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, mexican, russian, canadian
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, trike, helicopter, train
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the german##1
2. the german is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the russian is between the mexican and the canadian##2
5. the person driving the trike is the person driving the trike##1
6. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the helicopter and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | german | canadian | russian | mexican     |
| Transport     | subway | train  | trike   | helicopter |

