.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks, skydiving, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, adventure, animation, spy
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | woodworking | skydiving | writing | magic-tricks   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | animation | zombie      | spy |

