.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, rabbit, goat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, lacrosse, snowboarding, climbing
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | hamster | hedgehog   | rabbit      | goat      |
| Sport   | lacrosse     | snowboarding | parkour | climbing |

