.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, indie, house, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, american, british, japanese
1. the malaysian is on the right of the american##1
2. the fan of house is between the japanese and the american##2
3. the fan of indie is the american##1
4. the british is on the left of the american##1
5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the malaysian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | indie | house      | soul   |
| Nationality   | british  | american    | malaysian | japanese |

