.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, woodworking, sudoku, dancing
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, motorbike, car, quad-bike
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
6. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing | sudoku | dancing    | woodworking      |
| Transport   | car       | quad-bike       | motorbike | train |

