.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, japanese, colombian, argentine
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, dog, hedgehog
1. the japanese is on the far right##1
2. the brazilian is the brazilian##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the colombian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
6. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the argentine##3
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | colombian  | argentine | japanese |
| Pet           | dog     | hedgehog | rabbit    | rat     |

