.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, pepper, papaya, grapes
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, videographer, writer, engineer
1. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the videographer##3
2. the videographer is on the right of the writer##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the left of the scientist##1
4. the videographer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | pepper  | zucchini | grapes  | papaya      |
| Job    | engineer | scientist | writer | videographer |

