.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, drawing, reading, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, folk, ambient, disco
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of folk is the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
6. the fan of ambient is the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | drawing | filmmaking | reading | singing |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | soul       | folk   | ambient      |

