.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, water, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, rugby, surfing, parkour
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | 7up     | water          | coffee |
| Sport      | snowboarding | rugby | parkour | surfing  |

 